==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nonself
<hw>non"self`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
which is not oneself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Immunology)</fld> <def>Any material that enters the
body and is not recognized by the immune system as being part of its
body, thereby triggering an immune response; any material appearing to
the immune system to be foreign to its body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonsense</ent>⟦br⟧
